#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1697
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//eventList[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_JOB_SCRAPPER\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"Weary but excited, your scrappers make their way back to the ship, carrying "
"bags filled with a curious assortment of garbage. To your surprise, among "
"the heaps of trash, they have managed to salvage usable resources, a "
"testament to their resourcefulness. However, what truly captures their "
"attention is the massive amount of shiny trash, which seems to mesmerize "
"them. Despite its lack of practical value, their fascination serves as a "
"reminder that even in the bleakest of circumstances, finding joy and beauty "
"in the simplest things can be a source of resilience and inspiration."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1702
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//eventList[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_JOB_SCRAPPER\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your scrappers triumphantly return to the ship, carrying a box brimming with"
" valuable drone parts. Their discovery promises exciting possibilities for "
"enhancing your ship's capabilities in the face of imminent dangers lurking "
"in space."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1707
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//eventList[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_JOB_SCRAPPER\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"As you inquire about the source of the fuel they handed you, your scrappers "
"exchange nervous glances, evading your question. A sinking feeling settles "
"in as you realize the beacon outside has ceased transmitting—a sign that "
"their actions may have had unintended consequences. However, dwelling on the"
" past won't change anything, and you resign yourself to accepting the "
"situation."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1712
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//eventList[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_JOB_SCRAPPER\"]/event[4]/text"
msgstr ""
"With efficiency and expertise, your scrappers dismantle an entire piece of a"
" wrecked ship, transforming it into valuable scraps that can be repurposed "
"for repairs and upgrades. Among the salvaged materials, one of your "
"scrappers discovers a prized Protogen bobble-head, their joy evident on "
"their face. The discovery serves as a reminder that even amidst the grueling"
" work of survival, small moments of happiness can be found."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1717
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//eventList[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_JOB_SCRAPPER\"]/event[5]/text"
msgstr ""
"To your surprise, your scrappers return much later than anticipated, their "
"hands clutching a meager amount of scrap. Whether due to getting lost or a "
"cover-up for a less fruitful expedition, you can't help but wonder what "
"really transpired during their journey. Nonetheless, you accept their return"
" and the small contribution they managed to salvage, understanding that the "
"vastness of space often leads to unexpected challenges and detours."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1723
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//eventList[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_JOB_SCRAPPER\"]/event[6]/text"
msgstr ""
"With a sense of urgency, your scrappers finally return, their tardiness "
"heightening your awareness of the encroaching fleet. Though their hands hold"
" a meager amount of scrap, you understand that time is of the essence. Every"
" resource counts as you desperately attempt to stay one step ahead of the "
"pursuing forces, making the most of what you have and pushing the limits of "
"your ship's capabilities. The fleet draws nearer, and you steel yourself for"
" the challenges that lie ahead, knowing that every decision and every scrap "
"of resource could be the difference between survival and defeat."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1732
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//eventList[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_JOB_TRASH_COMPACT\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Trash Eater returns carrying several piles of garbage. You're not sure "
"what their origin is but you don't really care either."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1736
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//eventList[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_JOB_TRASH_COMPACT\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"It would seem a wrecked pirate ship was nearby, judging by the purple marks "
"on most of the metal that's been brought back."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1740
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//eventList[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_JOB_TRASH_COMPACT\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"Getting more salvage doesn't hurt at all. It doesn't this time either. You "
"do wonder why the Trash Eater has brought several protogen figurines back "
"with them, though. Maybe they thought they were neat."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1744
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//eventList[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_JOB_TRASH_COMPACT\"]/event[4]/text"
msgstr ""
"You're starting to wonder whether the Trash Eater will even return after "
"setting them free, but it seems they're back. And they've brought scrap! "
"What a sensible gift."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1748
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//eventList[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_JOB_TRASH_COMPACT\"]/event[5]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Trash Eater seems to have found so much machinery that he'd be able to "
"make something for you; what exactly do you want?"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1750
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//eventList[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_JOB_TRASH_COMPACT\"]/event[5]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1755
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//eventList[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_JOB_TRASH_COMPACT\"]/event[6]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Trash Eater returned extremely late and brought very little with them. "
"Even worse, you're sure the Fleet is creeping closer by the second."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1760
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//eventList[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_JOB_TRASH_COMPACT\"]/event[7]/text"
